{
  "stem": "21004.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I was drafted, a year before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was drafted a year before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then, a year later, they took me in the Army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the Polish Army, I had very good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was really-- tried to be, you know, like they say, a Jew doesn't like to go in the Polish Army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were paying off who can.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some people made themselves sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Years ago, they cut even fingers off, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- they didn't want to go to the Army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was strict.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Polish Army was very strict.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even they won the war in three weeks, but the uniforms and everything was so spotless, clean, nice.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the exercises, very rough, very rough.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But for me, it didn't mean nothing, because I was always not afraid of nothing, jumping or high or far.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was always-- made-- made the norm better than somebody else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I liked to ride the horses, so instead of going to the machinery, to the cannons, I wanted to go to the horses.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was not easy by the horses, but I loved it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So then I went to the horses and I was riding horses, and also, not only riding, I was making-- they called it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In Poland, [NON-ENGLISH] means you have tricks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "On the horses, you make tricks, all kinds of tricks, like you jump on the horse on the saddle from the back, jump on the saddle, cutting trees.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had trees put up, how many trees, so many hat you cut, you know, like-- actually, the caballeria used to be-- my cousin used to be in the caballeria, was strictly only horses, no cavalry at all.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So this, who cuts more, it's-- they give you a A, a B, whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
